    'body' => 'Jens "Spacejens" Rydholm wrote:
> 
> On Wed, 16 Sep 1998, David J. Golden wrote:
> 
> >       The launch tube doesn\'t carry vehicles, it launches them. You\'re
> > limited to a single craft per 30min turn from a regular hangar.
